"{\"uid\": \"toronto.citynews.ca-2024-05-15-paris-garbage-collectors-lift-strike-threat-ahead-of-olympic-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Adjust preferences  With your consent we may collect cookies and information to enhance our service, and improve your experience.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These cookies and data are essential for browsing our website and allowing services.\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Examples include, session, authentication, and security cookies.\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These cookies and data enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalized content.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These cookies and data inform us which pages are most informative and engaging via analytics.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These cookies may track data across websites for marketing and interest-based advertising to provide personalized content, offers, and advertisements.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Toronto  By The Associated Press  Posted May 15, 2024 6:52 am.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.333583873949502e-15, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last Updated May 15, 2024 6:56 am.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) - Paris garbage collectors have lifted the strike notice that threatened to leave the French capital facing piles of rubbish during the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999685605876, \"rank\": 3.1436604556979165e-08, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9980762745840552, \"rank\": 0.0011894546503788028, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris City Hall said Wednesday it had sealed a deal with the workers and that the strike notice covering several days in May and a period from July to Sept. 8 had been lifted.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympic Games will take place July 26-Aug. 11, followed by the Aug. 28-Sept. 8 Paralympics.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"An increase in the allowance system has been approved: 50 euros ($54) gross per month from July 2024, then 30 euros ($32.5) gross per month from January 2025,\\\" Paris City Hall said in a statement.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, the framework for bonuses for the workers who will be mobilized during the Olympic and Paralympic Games \\\"remains between 600 euros ($650) and 1,900 euros ($2,060), depending on the degree of intensification of the workload during the preparation, organization and/or participation in the staging\\\" of the event.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year,thousands of tons of rubbishremained on the Paris streets during a long strike by garbage collectors protesting a reform of the French pension system.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1753, \"end\": 1758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999